## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Execute `python src/preprocessing.py`, `python src/train.py`, and `python src/fairness_audit.py` to ensure local scripts run without errors.
- Validate metrics file/output is cleanly generated.

### Manual Verification
- Local run: `streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py`.
- Browser subagent will capture screenshots of the active "Fairness Audit" and "SHAP Explanations" pages as requested.
- Deploy to Streamlit Cloud using the browser agent and return the live URL.
